{"tid":2494052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然鄭文傑平時柒柒地，但佢今次冇講錯，的確係恐嚇。","createTime":"2021-04-18T11:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T11:39:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7536aae6c21758029957b5e39bfe2313ac3b1fc2","tid":2494052,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3003655309870540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F3003655309870540&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=f4e70492\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3003655309870540</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n雖然鄭文傑平時柒柒地，但佢今次冇講錯，個email的確係恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3003658096536928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F3003658096536928&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=7b6cc678\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3003658096536928</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑收到封信應該有起因嘅，例如佢同妻兒返鄉下過關比 Special Branch 周佢地促膝詳談之類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3004162736486464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F3004162736486464&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=bc3c9247\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/3004162736486464</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然鄭文傑平時柒柒地，但佢今次冇講錯，的確係恐嚇。而且封信應該有起因嘅，例如呀警司大人同妻兒返鄉下比 Special Branch 周佢地促膝詳談之類。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會咁認為呢，因為 BNO 簽證啱啱開波，簡單來講就係英國情報當局準備好晒黑名單，當然亦順手清算埋英國、澳洲公民做港區黑警班人渣。要知道 Home Office 係香港姑姐 Priti Patel 揸旗（遠遠超越香港之友），佢同我一樣咁喪，乜都做得出架。<br />\n<br />\n仲有內文亦有線索，我讀得出佢有被￼遺棄嘅心情，同妄想緊英國會突然間變返親中。"},{"pid":"d4fe13e77dfe64b3f7f67a0d8bd34d394ef5ae93","tid":2494052,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"英國情報部門捉哂班英國同鄉會先講"},{"pid":"4120209dc9a570fa67a622d0c6db0ae2bf08454c","tid":2494052,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0428%2F4a4fa442j00q9i5pq001lc000p800ixm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2020%252F0428%252F4a4fa442j00q9i5pq001lc000p800ixm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=25e09c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2020%2F0428%2F1062787cj00q9i5pq001kc000d000sgm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2020%252F0428%252F1062787cj00q9i5pq001kc000d000sgm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f392dcc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2e68258ae1ee19bdac19ce7f8ad73f032f1484b","tid":2494052,"uid":396949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"點解話佢平時柒柒地<br />\n佢唔係喺英國搞咗個香港同鄉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}